{"tid":511582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水貨支那蝗大鬧巴士站","createTime":"2017-12-27T15:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T16:04:45.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5d481a6f92c586204cc82d024e5660f408ec86ce","tid":511582,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"27/12 據悉因巴士座位及「行李儲存空間」（即係輪椅位）已滿，外勤人員以安全為由截龍，暫時阻止乘客登車。但有人因不滿安排，向外勤人員指罵，更搬出令壽堂問候一番。外勤人員反問對方何以𨳒人老母，就被對邊同行親瘦後指其粗言穢語。有其他外勤員工替同事不值，掏出手機拍攝了這片段。<br />\n<br />\n編按：蕃薯屎都未痾清，就當正自己皇帝？咁叻自己躝番上大陸丫！<br />\n<br />\n片段撮自車長Whatsapp群組。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: 柏斯敦巴士台 plaxtonl's Bus Page<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1542136319157397&amp;id=459548207416219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1542136319157397%26id%3D459548207416219&d=n8Z6aSXZwM1JKqRL2XGGNk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ab83bbd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1542136319157397&amp;id=459548207416219</a>"},{"pid":"d2f42712f0ebae380c91025f99f9048d2dddaf5d","tid":511582,"uid":148639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}